<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien hehpih I he zo puoi,
 A melma A ngaidam thei;
 A thutiem hi a sie thei puoi,
 Kumsawt chanin ei vawp thei,
 Mihing lungthim a kihei zing,
 Amah lungthim a det hi;
 A Cha thihna leh thawhkitna,
 Ziekin kei hing zing ingka.

[V2]
 2. Tu zanin ei vengin,
 Lalpa, lauhum lak apat;
 Van mithiengte'n ei veng uhen,
 Khawvak masangsieh in, Amen.

[V3]
 Doh is F

[V4]
 3. Na lopina cheng cheng mu dingin,
 Ka mit ei sukvak sak inla;
 Leisiet go thilpha haw cheng sangin,
 Kei a dingin a lulpen hi;
 Khawvel leh sum cheng cheng bei ina,
 Ka Pathien thu vang mang puo'n a;
 Kum khawsawt a hinna ding ei piei,
 Pathien mihing-a chang Isu'n.</lyrics>
<title>EBENEZER</title>
</song>